# Per-grammar configuration for the calc example. See stele/README.md.

# Give the statement list a readable subject in the "Assuming … complete" hedge
# (the auto-derived form would be "the stmts are complete").
[names]
stmts = statements

# Collapse the two infix operators into one label before the readable cap, so a
# state that accepts both reads "…, or an operator." A class only fires when >=2
# of its members are legal in the state, so a lone operator keeps its spelling.
[class an operator]
PLUS
STAR
